The George Brown College offers a full-time gemmology certificate program, which is the only one in Ontario. They have over 250 partnerships with the jewellery industry that help facilitate field education opportunities and an annual jewellery exhibit and awards show. The college is one of North America's largest and best-equipped jewellery schools.
